data.description: Nicely updated and maintained ranch style home in the NE. 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage which is currently used as a bedroom, but would convert right back to a garage.  Kitchen that features lots of storage with an eat in bar plus dining area. 2 beautifully updated bathrooms, one of which has a walk in shower. Primary bedroom has a walk in closet!  Flooring throughout the house is laminate and tile. Large RV parking area, plus a 17 X 17 deck in the back yard, and a storage shed. Call today for your private showing.
